data.description:
With views of the golf course from your deck, situated within a short distance to the club house, and just moments away from private trails and open space, you don't want to miss out on this unique property! This mountain home offers spacious living with 5 bedrooms, 4 bathrooms, and over 3,000 square feet of living space. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by vaulted ceilings and a cozy fireplace, setting the perfect ambiance for relaxation and entertaining. Immerse yourself in the magnificent views that surround this property, providing a true sense of serenity and tranquility.

Located in the coveted location of Hiwan, this home is nestled within a private golf course community. With close proximity to multiple mountain parks, you'll have direct access to outdoor adventures minutes from your doorstep. Situated on just under an acre, this lot provides ample space for outdoor activities and boasts a large 590 square foot wrap around deck and a flat usable landscape.

Inside, the open floor plan allows for effortless flow throughout the home. Enjoy hosting gatherings at your basement wet bar or cozy up by the second fireplace on chilly evenings. With plenty of parking spaces and a circular driveway, convenience is at your fingertips.

Don't miss your chance to experience mountain living at its finest. Contact me today to schedule a showing of this remarkable property!
